<P N="2">2 WHether this fresh encounter (contayning an hotch-potch of matters confusedlie shuffled together) hath found a better successe, co~cer|ning the pretended <HI>dispossession</HI> of <HI>Diuels</HI> by <HI>prayer</HI> and <HI>fasting,</HI> then any of the precedent particulars pro|pounded at large in those our former discourses.</P>
